	dnl ****************************************************************
	dnl *** Check for sched_setaffinity from glibc versions before   ***
	dnl *** 2.3.4. The older versions of the function only take 2    ***
	dnl *** parameters, not 3.                                       ***
	dnl ***                                                          ***
	dnl *** Because the interface change was not made in a minor     ***
